[resource]
script = ExtResource("1_78siu")
reagent_id = "Cl2"
title = "Chlorine"
body = "[b]Basic facts[/b]
[table=2]
[cell]Formula:[/cell][cell]Cl₂[/cell]
[cell]Element:[/cell][cell]Chlorine[/cell]
[cell]Atomic number:[/cell][cell]17[/cell]
[cell]Molar mass:[/cell][cell]70.9 g/mol[/cell]
[cell]State at room temperature:[/cell][cell]Gas[/cell]
[cell]Color:[/cell][cell]Yellow-green[/cell]
[cell]Smell:[/cell][cell]Strong, irritating odor[/cell]
[/table]
[b]Important properties[/b]
• Strong oxidizing agent.
• Toxic gas that can irritate the eyes and lungs.
[b]Where chlorine is found[/b]
• In salt (NaCl).
• In seawater.
• In many chloride minerals.
[b]Uses[/b]
• Disinfection of water (pools, drinking water).
• Production of PVC plastic.
• Used to make bleaches and cleaning products.
[b]Safety[/b]
Chlorine gas is poisonous and must be handled carefully."
